OL,4,CMike Ashley to step down from leading
OL,5,CSports Direct Group
OL,6, Sports Direct founder Mike Ashley is to
OL,7, step down from leading his retail
OL,8, empire and hand the reins to his future
OL,9, son-in-law.
OL,11,FThe board of Frasers Group, which also
OL,12,Fowns House of Fraser, said talks were
OL,13,Funder way for Michael Murray, 31, to
OL,14,Fsucceed the billionaire on 1 May 2022.
OL,16,FThe move would see Mr Ashley step down
OL,17,Ffrom as chief executive but remain on
OL,18,Fthe board as an executive director.
OL,20,FMr Ashley founded Sports Direct in 1982
OL,21,Fand retains 64% of the group.
